definitions.definition: The act of ascending ; an ascent .
examples: The ascension of the hot-air balloon gave us a better view.

definitions.definition: A transcendence of the material world ; a transition to a higher form, state, or plane of existence .
That which rises, as from distillation .
The act or process of ceasing to be an incel , generally by losing one's virginity /having sex , or entering a romantic relationship .

main_definition: The act of ascending ; an ascent .
